# WANTED FEATURES of 'AIMSICD'
------------------------------

Still too early to open up an Issue for your wanted feature?
Fret no more, just place it here and we'll have a look at it!
If your're lucky, some kind developer will add it. NO ETA's.

EXAMPLE:

* Be alive, look awesome smell like flowers. - DONE


Now it's your turn: Hit us with ideas!
--------------------------------------

* Always display the current ciphering indicator (A5/X). - WANTED
* Display warning about turned off voice call encryption. - WANTED
* Play notification sound if phone is still in airplane mode after X minutes. - WANTED
